      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it certainly shows its age. The exterior has several minor dings, some paint chips, and light scratches consistent with regular use, and the interior upholstery shows noticeable wear and some staining. Mechanically, the car starts up reliably and drives well, but the next owner should be prepared for some upcoming routine maintenance, such as a fresh set of tires and a brake service. It is a solid, honest car for someone who needs dependable transportation and isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection.",
