      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats are supple and free of wear, while every electronic component and safety feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule and climate-controlled storage. It drives with the precision and silence of a brand-new car. Complete with all original documentation, two keys, and a spotless service history, this is an uncompromising example for the most discerning buyer.",
      "price": 48500.0,
